the source of http://url.wxianfeng.com

short_url is like http://tinyurl.com/ or http://goo.gl/ or ...

short_url is developed by mongodb 1.4.4 + ruby 1.8.7 + haml 3.0.13 + sinatra 1.0

1,config db in mongoshort.rb

2,start sinatra app
>nohup ruby mongoshort.rb -e production &

more option see : http://github.com/sinatra/sinatra

3,start mongodb
>nohup mongodb/bin/mongod --dbpath=/usr/local/system/mongodb/data &

4,see siantra app and mongodb are started?
>netstat -antup

tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:27017               0.0.0.0:*                   LISTEN      25471/mongod
tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:4567                0.0.0.0:*                   LISTEN      25469/ruby

